<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.891984>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Molineus lotoris n. sp., parasite of Procyon lotor from Mexico. A: male, anterior end; B: male, frontal view; C: male, bursa; D: female, posterior region; E: male, synlophe at anterior body level; F: male, synlophe at mid-body level; G: male, synlophe at posterior body level; H: female, synlophe at anterior body level; I: female, synlophe at mid-body level; J: female, synlophe at posterior body level; scale bars 0.05 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/891984/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

